/*!
\page inspection_ismatrix ISMATRIX Test For a 2D Matrix

<p>
Section: \ref sec_inspection "Inspection Functions"
\section Usage
This function tests to see if the argument is a matrix.  The 
syntax for <tt>ismatrix</tt> is
\verbatim
   x = ismatrix(y)
\endverbatim
and it returns a logical 1 if the argument is size <tt>N x M</tt> or
<tt>M x N</tt> and a logical 0 otherwise.
*/
